Why CSG?



What dress code?

	                    	We want our employees to be comfortable and dress in whatever will allow them to perform at their best.
	                    



Ownership

	                    	At CSG, employees have opportunity to become shareholders of CSG. Share in the growth and success of the company both as an employee and owner.
	                    



Health & Wellness

	                    	Choose a plan that is right for you with offerings of High Deductible Health Plans as well as your more traditional PPO.
	                    



Financial Security

	                    	Let us help you meet your financial goals. CSG savings plan includes 4% match, immediate vesting and a Roth IRA to help you fund your retirement dreams.
	                    



Progressive Time Off

	                    	CSG offers a spectrum of generous time off plans and leave options in support of the ever-evolving life-landscape. Ranging from 16 weeks of paid parental leave with supplemental adoption assistance to unlimited vacation days (USA), CSG is committed to providing progressive avenues for taking a timeout to focus on family, travel or simply rejuvenate.
						



Globalize your Experience

							With 20+ offices around the world plus remote opportunities, you will have the potential to interact and learn with many different cultures. 
						











Our Impact
Globally, our 3,300+ employees manage many aspects of a communication service provider’s (CSPs) revenue and customer management systems and processes. From the initial activation and support of customer accounts and services, to the monetization of premium digital content, cybersecurity operations, and all the way to bill presentment, payments and accounts receivables management, our billing and mediation services support the majority of the world’s top 100 CSPs.



