				About CSG International			




					In today’s dynamic and competitive marketplace, one thing is certain: change. As one of the world’s leading providers of business support solutions, CSG International understands what it means to evolve, adapt and transform. Our goal is to help you generate revenue, maximize customer value, and manage your business more efficiently.
				


				CSG helps companies around the world succeed every day—and we continue to evolve our portfolio of market-leading solutions to meet ever-changing market demands.
			

				CSG helps businesses compete—and win. We do this with:
			


An extensive portfolio. Our market-leading solutions and services support your business objectives, including revenue management, customer interaction management, and analytics and intelligence.
				

Industry knowledge and expertise. We have experience across a wide range of vertical markets—including cable television and direct broadcast satellite, fixed-line and mobile telecommunications, financial services, utilities, media/entertainment and more.
				

Flexible solution delivery models. We've designed our solutions to fit your individual business objectives, including on-premise software, service bureau, and managed services, all delivered and supported by our global professional services team.
				

Diverse experience. We've deployed solutions in emerging, established and mature markets worldwide for more than 30 years.
				


				The markets CSG supports face unprecedented change.
				Whether you are a mobile provider in São Paulo, a broadband operator in New York, or content provider in Singapore, customers dictate what services are introduced, how they are delivered, and what they expect in exchange for brand loyalty.
			

				We know time is of the essence. Markets are changing rapidly. Revenue opportunities ebb and flow quickly. Customers demand more of you in return for loyalty. And the services and technologies that support your customers are increasingly complex.
			

				You are not alone in this dynamic marketplace. CSG is here to help you accelerate business—anywhere.
			





