			Company Description 


			CSG Systems International, Inc. engages in providing business support solutions serving the communications industry. Its products and solutions include cable and satellite care & billing, content management & monetization, convergent rating and billing, mediation and data management, and wholesale s...
		


                CSG Systems International, Inc. engages in providing business support solutions serving the communications industry. Its products and solutions include cable and satellite care & billing, content management & monetization, convergent rating and billing, mediation and data management, and wholesale settlement and routing. The company was founded on October 17, 1994 and is headquartered in Englewood, CO.
            




